Rating: 3
A great recipe. The sweetness and richness of the prunes works excellently with the pork. I made a few amendments stricly based on the lack of certain ingredients at the time of cooking the meal. I used a Pinot Blanc instead of the Pinot Gris and combined the thyme with some tarragon which paired nicely. I also only had regular anise to work with, although I believe it would worked better with star anise. All in all it was a great recipe. I will definitely make this dish again

